1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
Here's what science actually says about sterilizing immunity.

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:06,000
Sterilizing immunity means complete protection against infection.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:08,400
But how does it really work?

4
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:13,200
When your body fights off a virus, it can develop this immunity.

5
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:15,200
But it’s not always guaranteed.

6
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:20,400
Some vaccines can provide sterilizing immunity, meaning they stop the virus from replicating.

7
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:24,000
But emerging research shows not all infections trigger this.

8
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,600
It’s a complex game.

9
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,400
Want to unlock more secrets of immunity?

10
